Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:28.22,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What is most precious to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:31.87,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But when I wondered how to make it come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:35.27,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I stopped because I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.47,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One day an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:42.10,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Suddenly landed in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:45.53,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Although it was different from what I imagined,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:48.91,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I slowly raised my arms towards it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:52.20,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One clumsy step forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:56.04,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Can change the world in a flash
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.29,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What's waiting for me? What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:03.32,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Gather courage and move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:08.04,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm no longer the insignificant me of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.90,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Since I've started to play my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:14.72,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The curtain rises, what awaits beyond
