Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.98,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even what I thought was impossible will come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:28.40,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll make my glittering hopes resound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:35.50,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So that it can be heard everywhere, my symphony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:41.86,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I could send a message
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:45.55,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}To the hesitant me from the past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:49.00,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I would tell her "I'm having fun now!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.41,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}After all, my heart is beating this fast
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.62,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That girl who seems able to do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.48,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That girl who never stops laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:02.68,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Despite being worried, despite feeling lost
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.77,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}She never loses sight of her dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:11.48,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In order to someday find
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:14.70,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The perfect phrase for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.77,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if it's the first time, I'll take the challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:21.27,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Please let my prayer reach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:25.21,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I listened carefully to the melody
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.31,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That is being played someplace faraway
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:31.75,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's open the door to the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:38.95,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I won't ever let this symphony end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:55.82,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I join together my right hand's little finger and my left hand's little finger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.21,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}While I make myself a promise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:05.03,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}"I will never forget these feelings"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:09.68,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm no longer the insignificant me of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.95,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Since I've started to play my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.42,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The curtain rises, what awaits beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.64,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Is the stage that I drew in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:23.45,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If I take a step towards it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.50,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even what I thought was impossible will come true
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.94,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll make my glittering hopes resound
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:33.37,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's make them spread everywhere
Comment: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:37.20,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Rarara rarara rarara saa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.20,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}C'mon!
Comment: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.77,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Rarara rarara rarara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:43.85,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Towards a new me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:50.78,EN - Liella!,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The symphony is starting now
